---
import programsImage from "../assets/programs.png";
---

<section class="bg-[#FAF7F2] py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-14 px-5 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[0.92fr_1.08fr] lg:gap-16">
    <div>
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#D97706] sm:text-sm">
        Why Volunteer
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#1F2937] sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl">
        Children remember the people who kept showing up.
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-[#1F2937]/70 md:text-xl md:leading-9">
        Volunteering with Children First is not about having every answer. It is about offering steady encouragement, helping a child feel seen and becoming part of a community that believes opportunity should be close to every child.
      </p>
    </div>

    <img
      src={programsImage.src}
      alt="Children learning with support from volunteers"
      class="h-[500px] w-full rounded-[2rem] object-cover sm:h-[680px] lg:rounded-[3rem]"
    />
  </div>
</section>
